Add your steps (pseudo-code) for the dice game here.
Display the welcome page
Ask to start the game

While the game is going
    pick two random numbers between 1 and 6 and output the sum

    if the sum is 7 or 11 then output win_screen and ask if they want to play again

    else if the sum is 2 0r 3 or 12 then output the lose_screen and ask if they want to play again

    else make player_point = to the sum and ask player to roll again

    if the player point is greater than 0
    
    then let player roll again 
    
    if sum is equal to player point or 7 output win_screen and ask if they want to play again

    else let player roll again

